# Enumeration ExporterType

Exporter types for telemetry data

#### Description

Defines where telemetry data is sent

##### Index

### Enumeration Members

LOCAL REMOTE

## Enumeration Members

### LOCAL

LOCAL: "LOCAL"

Local exporter - data stays on the local machine

#### Description

Useful for development, debugging, or local analysis

### REMOTE

REMOTE: "REMOTE"

Remote exporter - data sent to remote telemetry service

#### Description

Production-ready, sends data to configured endpoint
